<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ذ ك ر<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٩٦٨ - ذ ك ر]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>اذَّكَّرَ يذَّكَّر، فهو مُذَّكِّر، والمفعول مُذَّكَّر <span class="c2">(للمتعدِّي)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• اذَّكّر الشَّخصُ:</span> اتّعظ واعتبر <span class="c1">" <span class="c3">{وَمَا يُدْرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُ يَزَّكَّى. أَوْ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنْفَعَهُ الذِّكْرَى}</span> "</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• اذَّكَّر الشَّيءَ:</span> استحضره، واسترجعه في ذهنه <span class="c1">" <span class="c3">{وَلَقَدْ صَرَّفْنَا فِي هَذَا الْقُرْءَانِ لِيَذَّكَّرُوا}</span> "</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>